Build the Docker image mt-scan-base (with cuda) : `docker build -t mt-scan-base -f docker/Dockerfile.base --build-arg ENABLE_CUDA=ON .`оБЦоАїоГБоГїоГєоДЭ

Build the Docker image mt-scan-base (without  cuda) : `docker build -t mt-scan-base -f docker/Dockerfile.base .`

Build the Docker image mt-scan  : `docker build -t mt-scan -f docker/Dockerfile --build-arg USER_ID=$(id -u) --build-arg GROUP_ID=$(id -g) .`оБЦоАїоГБоГїоГєоДЭ

Enter container (with GPU access): `docker run -it --rm --gpus all -v /opt/mt-scan:/workspace mt-scan`

Enter container (without GPU access): `docker run -it --rm -v ~/mt-scan:/workspace mt-scan`

Build the project (without CUDA): `cmake -S . -B build -GNinja && cmake --build build`

Build the project (with CUDA): `cmake -S . -B build -GNinja -DUSE_CUDA=ON && cmake --build build`